# Findings & Business Insights

## Project Overview

This project analyzed 862 home surveillance and smart security product listings to identify revenue drivers, demand patterns, inventory trends, seller performance, and product category opportunities within the home surveillance e-commerce market.

---

# Executive Summary

The analysis revealed that revenue and demand are concentrated among a relatively small number of brands, product categories, and sellers.

Smart surveillance products generated the largest share of marketplace revenue, while several leading brands consistently appeared among the top performers across revenue, sales volume, and inventory availability.

The findings suggest that product demand, category positioning, and seller reach are major contributors to marketplace performance.

